docs.lead_paragraph: FIRES IN CINCINNATI--A HEROINE.--One of the most destructive confiagrations with which our city has been visited, occurred Saturday morning. The fire broke out in WILL'S carriage shop, and is supposed to have been the work of an incendiary.
